(program-wide)
=============Only in src: main0.cpp
-:
 +CTRL					- Navigate Backwards
+:
 +CTRL					- Navigate Forward
I:
 +CTRL					- Show Input Line
N:
 +CTRL					- New Document
O:
 +CTRL					- Show Output
P:
 +CTRL					- Show Preferences
